data.description: This spacious single-family home offers a generous living space with 2,618 square feet. It includes a huge Master bedroom with his and her closets, big bathroom with separate garden tub & shower. The other 2 bedrooms are also over sized with big walk in closets. The house offers an open floorplan, creating a spacious and interconnected living area that allows for versatility in interior design and a sense of openness. Featuring A additional bonus room included in the layout, complete with air conditioning, offering flexibility for use as a home office, playroom, or any other desired purpose. The dining area is notably spacious, providing ample room for hosting family dinners or entertaining guests. In addition to the formal dining area, there is a sizable breakfast room where you can enjoy casual meals and morning coffee. The home has undergone recent renovations, including updates such as granite countertops in kitchen and master bath. High end  stainless steel appliances, subway tile, and laminate flooring. These modern touches enhance both the functionality and aesthetics of the space. The interior has been freshly painted, providing a clean and appealing canvas for personalization and decorating. The roof is relatively new and replaced in 2016. Upgraded Spray foam insulation 2018. Extended driveway for flexible parking. The home also features, beautiful lush landscaping with big trees for shade. Home also includes a big storage shed. With its strategic location near the Randolph Airforce base, proximity to shopping centers, nearby schools, and the added benefit of a community park and playground, this home at 8343 Northaven Dr offers a well-rounded and family-oriented living experience in Converse, TX. Please schedule a showing today.
